#text=I got the cake mix , eggs , oil , measuring cups and a baking pan from my pantry .
#text=I got a mixing bowl from my cupboard and a large wooden spoon from my drawer .
#text=I poured the cake mix from the package into the bowl .
#text=I added two eggs , and used my measuring cups to add oil and water to the bowl .
#text=I mixed the ingredients thoroughly until they were smooth .
#text=I got my baking pan and sprayed it with cooking spray .
#text=I poured the cake batter into the pan and placed it into the oven .
#text=I waited 30 minutes until the cake was slightly brown and I took it out of the oven .
#text=I allowed it to sit on the counter and cool until I could put the icing on .
#text=I got opened the container of icing and used a spatula to spread it on the cake .
#text=This is how I baked a cake .
